      	<div class="block_header"><h3>CURRENT CAMPAIGN</h3></div>
  			<div class="image_block"><a href=""><img src="/media/uploads/campaign_image/DrKing300.png" /></a></div>
  			<div class="txt_block">
  				<h4><a href="/campaign/execorderpolicing/">President Obama: End discriminatory, violent policing and its unjust consequences</a></h4>
  				<p>There is an epidemic of racial bias, police violence, and a lack of accountability in our country's police forces. Thousands have been killed. Millions more have been sucked into the criminal justice system by racially-biased practices. 
                <a href="/campaign/execorderpolicing/"><span class="">More &raquo;</span></a></p>
